  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Embrace & Master the Chaos!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brick-breaking action, re-imagined and realized to its fullest potential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bricks are falling! Threatening your home planet! Aim carefully and bounce your ball, weaponize your ship or discover unique methods to defend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Break Bricks.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every stage brings fresh challenges with new brick types, patterns, and mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master your aim and adapt to the increasing complexity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/fc019cae72ac86ffc5669bb3921b9d5c.poster.avif?t=1755282063\" width=800 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/fc019cae72ac86ffc5669bb3921b9d5c.webm?t=1755282063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/fc019cae72ac86ffc5669bb3921b9d5c.mp4?t=1755282063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Break the Enemy.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s not just the bricks you have to deal with. Some enemies block your ball, others target your ship, and a few play dirty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/db607600d3a723149d1d203498997afa.poster.avif?t=1755282063\" width=664 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/db607600d3a723149d1d203498997afa.webm?t=1755282063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/db607600d3a723149d1d203498997afa.mp4?t=1755282063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level Up.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a randomized selection of perks at every level. Experiment with synergies and craft a build that suits your play-style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/abb1ff57d0c2993da3c23fcbfcb5868c.poster.avif?t=1755282063\" width=760 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/abb1ff57d0c2993da3c23fcbfcb5868c.webm?t=1755282063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/abb1ff57d0c2993da3c23fcbfcb5868c.mp4?t=1755282063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Break. Die. Repeat.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Over is just a new beginning. Use the coins, gems, and gifts you collect to unlock new ships, balls, and abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run makes you stronger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/6e41d2aea1a2dcba59b81bf16779e316.poster.avif?t=1755282063\" width=524 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/6e41d2aea1a2dcba59b81bf16779e316.webm?t=1755282063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/6e41d2aea1a2dcba59b81bf16779e316.mp4?t=1755282063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play Your Way.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From hardcore mode to relaxing zen mode, from Aim Arena to Daily Challenges, there’s a mode for every mood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/f85df7f9b47273c405640d038e529263.avif?t=1755282063\" width=568 height=176 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Small in Size. Big on Fun.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rogue Bricks is just few hundred megabytes packed with endless entertainment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From desktop to in-game takes only handful of seconds </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/e50008dc93df9cb3ea2a2c215ec2cce9.poster.avif?t=1755282063\" width=800 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/e50008dc93df9cb3ea2a2c215ec2cce9.webm?t=1755282063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/e50008dc93df9cb3ea2a2c215ec2cce9.mp4?t=1755282063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
